metadata.name: Here // There // Where
metadata.description:
Where do I belong? Where do I go from here? 
Alone in a distorted city
Where is the place where I belong?

PNG, 3975 x 2789 px
Made using ink on paper & colored using Procreate

Cityscape Illustration by Aysa Putri (aysaptr)

Originally created in 26th of February 2022
Jakarta, Indonesia
